        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2013-11-24 20:14:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/e14a714c-553b-11e3-aac4-52540035b04c).  Ran 27 tests.  6 tests failed: sanity-scrub, sanity-lfsck, lustre-rsync-test, replay-single, sanityn, sanity.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
